 \{ans_rule(10) \} \( cm \) . $BR
Find the value of the area 
 \{ans_rule(10) \} \( cm ^2 \) . $BR
Find the value of the perimeter 
 \{ans_rule(10) \} \( cm \) . $BR
 $BR

$PAR
EOT

ANS( num_cmp( $L1, reltol=>1 ) );
ANS( num_cmp( $H1, reltol=>1 ) );
